    <title>【分享】查看sqlserver2008中当前正在执行的任务</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2015/12/01/view-current-running-job-on-sqlserver2008/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2015/12/01/view-current-running-job-on-sqlserver2008/</id>
